    "id": "fc7745621070b1e2",
    "source": "page",
    "url": "https://ceconline.edu/academics/departments",
    "title": "Departments - College of Engineering Chengannur",
    "section": "Department of Basic Science & Language",
    "text": "Computer Science & Engineering is an academic program that incorporates the various technical areas of computational hardware and software studies. Electrical engineering is a professional engineering discipline that equip engineers to work in the field of the critical infrastructure ie. the Power sector that includes Generation, Distribution and Utilization of electric power, integrate renewable energy systems, manage smart grid systems, and be the key persons in this era of Electric Vehicles. Electronics and Communication Engineering is the study of electronics to facilitate communications and solve engineering problems. General Engineering is a dynamic discipline poised to tackle multifaceted challenges across industries. Its blend of theoretical knowledge and practical skills prepares students to contribute meaningfully to technological advancement and societal progress. Computer science and engineering is an academic program at some universities that integrates the fields of computer engineering and computer science.",
    "metadata": {
      "type": "page",
      "tags": [
        "courses",
        "facilities"
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "886830bd0a386763",
    "source": "page",
    "url": "https://ceconline.edu/about/facilities",
    "title": "Facilities - College of Engineering Chengannur",
    "section": "Transporation",
    "text": "The college is fully equipped with well furnished smart class rooms. The college also has laptops which are issued to the students to help them in their project work. Other facilities include Diesel Generator System to power the whole college, Power Backups, Water Purifier System, Camera surveillance etc. There is also a Co-operative store adjacent to the college office which provides students with stationery and general provisions.The college owned men’s hostel and ladies’ hostel can house over 100 inmates and provide a nourishing environment. The College Library has a wide collection of latest books, periodicals, and CDs. College of Engineering, Chengannur is one of the 18 engineering colleges equipped with Mini Fablab. The College operates buses for the convenience of students and staff coming from in and around Salem city.",
    "metadata": {
      "type": "page",
