    "title": "B.Tech-Admissions - College of Engineering Chengannur",
    "section": "B .TECH (Lateral Entry)",
    "text": "Admission to UG programmes except in NRI seats is on the basis of the All Kerala Common Entrance Examination, conducted by the Commissioner for Entrance Examinations (CEE), Govt. of Kerala. The criteria for B.Tech degree admission is prescribed by the CEE, Govt. of Kerala and concerned University, and is issued every year by Govt. of Kerala through common prospectus for admission to professional degree courses. The entrance examinations are conducted usually in the month of April. Annual Intake for Full Time B.Tech UG Courses are :",
