  {
    "id": "bc14f511fc3558a6",
    "source": "page",
    "url": "https://ceconline.edu/2023/06/29/forcego",
    "title": "FORCEGO - College of Engineering Chengannur",
    "section": "Alumini",
    "text": "” FORCEGO ” is developed using the powerful Python language, incorporates advanced features such as Text-to-Speech (TTS), Google Text-to-Speech (gTTS), and Text Recognition features. These groundbreaking technologies work harmoniously to provide a seamless and inclusive experience, enabling the app to read out texts from various sources, including PDFs and images, in the user’s native language. Also ” ForceGo ” becomes the first-ever application to offer real-time translation into Malayalam language. With its user friendly graphical user interface , FORCEGO analyze and extract text from images, enabling visually impaired individuals to access content that was previously inaccessible.",
    "metadata": {
      "type": "page",
      "tags": [
        "admission"
      ]
    }
  },
