    "title": "Prof. (Dr.) Hari. V S - College of Engineering Chengannur",
    "section": "meta",
    "text": "Dr. Hari V S graduated in Electronics and Communication Engineering from TKM College of Engineering, Kollam in 1994. He joined the College of Engineering Chengannur in the year 1996. He obtained his M.Tech in Communications Systems from Indian Institute of Technology, Madras in 2006 and his Ph.D. from the School of Engineering ,Cochin University of Science and Technology in 2013.",
