    "text": "Amalu Susan Santhosh, student of S6 CSE and Secretary of IEEE Student Branch College of Engineering Chenganur, has been a source of strength and empowerment and an exemplary personality serving tremendously for the progress of Student Branch and for upholding the reputed name of the college. She is also a good mentor and an amazing speaker. Her extremely dedicated passion for experiencing new ventures and attaining higher skies has been inspiration to many. She has been awarded the much-deserved Google’s APAC Women Techmakers Scholarship and Grace Hopper Celebrations India Scholarship in 2018.",
