    "url": "https://ceconline.edu/2023/04/27/maker-station",
    "title": "MAKER STATION - College of Engineering Chengannur",
    "section": "Alumini",
    "text": "The Maker Station, an innovative and exciting program organized by Tinkerhub Foundation in partnership with Amazon India, which is an iteration of our popular program, Learning Stations. We are excited to share that the College of Engineering, Chengannur has been selected as one of the venue.Tinkerhub CE Chengannur in collaboration with the Training and Placement Cell of the College of Engineering Chengannur has acted as the venue organisers. This was an opportunity to be a part of one of the largest learning programs in the state which brings together students and makers from various backgrounds to showcase their creativity, skills, and passion for technology.",
