    "url": "https://ceconline.edu/academics/departments/department-of-applied-sciences",
    "title": "Department of Basic Science & Language - College of Engineering Chengannur",
    "section": "MAKER STATION",
    "text": "The department of Basic Science and Language is pivotal to the college’s academic framework, furnishing students with vital knowledge and skills necessary for excelling in various engineering disciplines. Offering a diverse array of subjects, the department forms the foundational core of engineering education. The department covers areas such as: Engineering Physics, Engineering Chemistry, Linear Algebra and Calculus, Graph Theory, Life Skills, Professional Communication, Industrial Economics and Foreign Trade. Together these subjects provide a comprehensive education that prepares students for the challenges of the engineering world, fostering analytical thinking, problem-solving skills and a global perspective. The Department of Basic Science and Language is dedicated to offering a rigorous and relevant curriculum, ensuring students are well- prepared to contribute to the advancement of technology and society. Smt. Moni P John Head Of the Department Department of Basic Science & Language College of Engineering, Chengannur Alappuha (Dist.) – 689121",
