    "url": "https://ceconline.edu/academics/departments/general_engineering",
    "title": "Department of General Engineering - College of Engineering Chengannur",
    "section": "MAKER STATION",
    "text": "General Engineering is a diverse field applying scientific principles and mathematical methodologies to design, develop, and maintain various structures, machinery, and systems. The curriculum offered by the department encapsulates a wide array of subjects, such as Engineering Graphics, Engineering Mechanics, Basic Mechanical Engineering, Basic Civil Engineering, Management for Engineers, and Sustainable Engineering. These courses are meticulously designed to lay a solid foundation, equipping students with the necessary theoretical knowledge and analytical skills. Hands-on workshops and CAD courses complement theoretical learning, fostering practical skills essential for addressing real-world challenges across industries. Dr. Ashok Kumar T V Head Of the Department Department of General Engineering College of Engineering, Chengannur Alappuzha (Dist.) – 689121",
