    "source": "page",
    "url": "https://ceconline.edu/2020/03",
    "title": "March 2020 - College of Engineering Chengannur",
    "section": "Corona Battalion: Student curates a system to aid the fight against the virus",
    "text": "The NSS unit of CEC banded together to build a home in a swift manner for their homeless classmate. IGNITE is a two-year technical outreach program initiated and organized by the IEEE Student Branch, College of Engineering, Chengannur (CEC) as an extension of the WIE STAR Program for the students of secondary schools. Aswin Mohan of College of Engineering, Chengannur developed an app to coordinate the services provided to people who are under observation at homes with COVID-19 symptoms.",
