    "title": "atfirst.pdf",
    "section": "page 1",
    "text": "Action taken report of the first IQAC held on 19-10-2019 As per the decisions of the first IQAC meeting held on 19-10-2019, the following actions have been taken. 1) An Industry institute Interaction cell (IIIC) and an Intellectual property right cell (IPR) have been constituted. Dr. Hari VS, Associate professor EC and Sri Philip Cherian, Associate professor EC have been appointed as the coordinators of IIIC cell and IPR cell respectively. 2) The HOD’s conducted class wise advisory meetings. The grievances and suggestions from students have been taken and addressed. 3) All co curricular activities and extra curricular of the college were brought under a common forum. The Google doc format for all activities is made available in the college website. 4) The IIIC cell has been entrusted to organize training and workshops for students and faculty. 5) HOD’s and module coordinators are authorized to evaluate the quality of question papers for series exams.",
