 filled on the basis of the Kerala State Rank List of NEET-UG 2025 prepared by the CEE, only those candidates satisfying the eligibility conditions as per Clauses 6 and 9.7.5(ii) & 9.7.5(iii) will be considered. In the case of candidates whose admissions are governed by inter-se merit list, only those candidates who figure in the Kerala State Rank List of 22 KEAM-2025, © CEE, TVM",
