support of the claim, to the online application. [Refer Annexure III (2)] (ii) Degree holders in BDS (DM): One seat in the MBBS course is reserved for holders of BDS on rotation basisin one of the colleges in the order of TVM, KLM, PTM, ALP, KTM, IDM, CMC, TCM, MLP, KKM, KNM vide G.O (Ms) No. 101/2023/H&FwD Dated: 28.04.2023 for the candidates having BDS degree recognised by any one of the Universities in Kerala, subjected to the eligibility conditions under clause 6. Admission to the course is based 26 KEAM-2025, © CEE, TVM",
