ng that the annual family income of the applicant is not more than Rs.6 lakhs for KEAM-2025. Dependants are the son/daughter/brother/sister of Fishermen. Candidates seeking admission under this quota will be eligible for fee concession, only if they upload the certificate in the prescribed format in Annexure XXXIV from Fisheries Officer of Kerala Fishermen Welfare Fund Board concerned (see clause 12.1.3 and Annexure VII (4). Note:-Certificate received after the prescribed time limit will not be entertained. 29 KEAM-2025, © CEE, TVM",
