 for academic merit will be added to the marks obtained by the respective candidates in the respective Entrance Examinations (provided they are ranked in the concerned Entrance Examination), computed out of 500 so that the candidates would be eligible for a maximum of 1000 marks. The merit list for each of the above category would be prepared on the basis of inter-se merit of the candidate as computed above. 31 KEAM-2025, © CEE, TVM",
