rity. Generally, candidates who have a minimum of 40% disability alone will be eligible to apply for this quota. Candidates seeking admission to Medical Courses (except BHMS course) will have to satisfy the eligibility criteria prescribed by the National Medical Commission of India for ‘Persons with Disabilities’ [See Annexure XXIV(i)] and for BHMS course the candidate 35 KEAM-2025, © CEE, TVM",
