 Quota: (a) Candidates claiming reservation under Scheduled Castes/Scheduled Tribes quota should upload the caste/community certificate from the Tahsildar concerned, in the prescribed proforma specifically meant for them to the online application (Format is given in Annexure XXIX). SC/ST caste status of children, whose parents contracted Inter-caste marriage, will be subject to the orders/clarification issued in G.O.(Ms) No. 25/2005/SCSTDD dated: 20.06.2005, judgement dated 10.08.2005 of the Full Bench of the Hon’ble High Court of Kerala in WP(C) 2483/2005 and connected cases and GO (Ms) No.109/2008/SCSTDD dated 20.11.2008.As per G.O.(MS) 38 KEAM-2025, © CEE, TVM",
