s, Chemistry and Biology/Bio-Technology taken together in qualifying examinations shall be 40% instead of 50%. (ii) In the case of BAMS/ BHMS/BSMS/BUMS courses, candidates belonging to SC/ST or SEBC, the minimum marks obtained in Physics, Chemistry and Biology taken together in qualifying examination shall be 40% instead of 50%. In respect of candidates included in the PD quota list published by the Commissioner for Entrance Examinations the minimum 52 KEAM-2025, © CEE, TVM",
