urisdiction of the Hon'ble High Court of Kerala. 14.3 Any other items not specifically covered in this prospectus will be decided by the CEE and the decision shall be final. 14.4 Preventive measures against ragging: According to the Kerala Prohibition of Ragging Act, 1998, 'ragging' means doing of any act by disorderly conduct to a student of an educational 105 KEAM-2025, © CEE, TVM",
