    "section": "page 1",
    "text": "MINUTES OF SECOND IQAC MEETING Venue : Conference room Date: 25.01.2020 Members Present 1. Dr. Jacob Thomas V ,Principal ,CE Chengannur-IQAC Chair person 2. Mr. Bony Thomas ,Scientist E, Electronics Regional Test Laboratory -Member Industry 3. Mr. Biju C Thomas, Chief consultant &Managing Director, Prime builders &Architects, Chengannur 4. Mrs. Deepa A K ,Secretary, WIE Affinity Group IEEE Kerala Section. 5. Mr. Muhammed Rabeeh N, Co-Founder Electree Energy Solutions –Member Alumini 6. Dr. Jyothiraj VP ,HOD EC Department 7. Dr.Smitha Dharan ,HOD CS Department 8. Dr. DeepaJ, Professor, EC Department ,IQAC coordinator 9. Mr. Jayadeep Kumar J, Assistant Professor, Mechanical Engg, IQAC Asst.coordinator 10. Ms.Deepa Susan J, Assistant Professor,Department of Electronics ,IIIC Member 11. Mrs. RenuKK,Associate Professor ,Mathematics ,IQAC member 12. Mrs. Savitha K P,Assistant Professor, Electrical Engg,IQAC member 13. Mrs. JyothiRL,Assistant Professor, Computer Engg.,IQAC member,IPRC member 14. Mrs.Manjusha S Nair Assistant Professor, Computer Engg.,Placement officer 15. Mr. Ayoobkhan T E ,Associate Professor, EC Department ,NBA coordinator 16. Ms.Swathi Krishna O ,S8 CS ,IEEE representative 17. Karthik Krishna,s6 CS ,Placement Representative 18. Libin Mathew Varghese,S6EEE,IEEE Representative Agenda 1. Review of KTU external audit 2. Academic calendar 2020 Even semester 3. NBA Accreditation status 4. IIIC and IPR action plan 5. Placement statistics 6. Professional membership and Industrial training for faculty 7. Professional bodies (IEEE, IEDC) activities. The meeting started at 2.30 pm. Principal welcomed IQAC members and the special invitees.The agenda was unanimously approved. Principal briefed the action taken report of the last IQAC meeting and also the auditor’s remarks of academic audit 2019-20 odd semester. The academic calendar and major events scheduled for the current semester were discussed. The NBA accreditation coordinator reviewed the steps taken for uploading prequalifier for various departments. He mentioned the need of collecting the professional profile of alumina for reviewing the department specific vision and mission.",
