    "section": "page 1",
    "text": "COLLEGE OF ENGINEERING CHENGANNUR Minutes of the External IQAC meeting held on 18.03.2022 Online Platform: Google Meet Time.2pm Minutes of the IQAC meeting Members Present 1. Dr. Smitha Dharan, Principal, CE Chengannur-IQAC Chair person 2. Mr. Bony Thomas, Scientist E, Electronics Regional Test Laboratory -Member Industry 3. Mr. Biju C Thomas, Chief consultant &Managing Director, Prime builders &Architects, Chengannur 4. Mrs. Deepa A K, Secretary, WIE Affinity Group IEEE Kerala Section. 5. Mr. Muhammed Rabeeh N, Co-Founder Electree Energy Solutions –Member Alumini 6. Dr. Laila D, HOD EC Department 7. Dr.Manju S Nair, HOD CS Department 8.Dr. Rajesh VG,HOD General Engineering 9. Dr.Raju M, Placement officer 10. Dr Madhusoodhanan Nair, HOD Applied science Department 11.. Mr.Vinod PR, Assistant Professor, Computer Engg ,PTA Secretary 12. Dr. DeepaJ, Professor, EC Department, IQAC coordinator 13. Mrs. RenuKK, Associate Professor, Mathematics, IQAC member 14. Mrs. Savitha K P, Assistant Professor, Electrical Engg,IQAC member 15. Mrs. Jyothi RL, Assistant Professor, Computer Engg.,IQAC member,IPRC member 16.Mrs.RajiA, Assistant Professor, Electronics Engineering ,IQAC member 17. Mrs. Nisha Rajan S, Assistant Professor, Electronics Engineering ,IQAC member 18.Mrs.Sherin Joseph Assistant Professor, Electrical Engg,IQAC member 19. Rishikesh K V, Student representative Agenda 1. Review of academic activities and placement statistics of odd semester 2021-2022 2. Progress of NBA accreditation activities 3. Internal IQAC audit status 4. Quality improvement initiatives and action plans 5. Other relevant presented by the chair Meeting stated at 2 PM with the welcome speech by the IQAC coordinator. IQAC chair presented the Institution details like admission status of 2022, commencement of classes of various semesters, result analysis of previous semesters, placement statistics of 2021 pass-out and current final year students (2022 batch) and current academic activities. The chair also presented the achievements and award obtained by IEEE and IEDC. Accreditation Coordinator presented the status of accreditation activities by the institution. He also presented the details regarding the facilities to be incorporated as the part of accreditation process. The IQAC coordinator presented the institution IQAC activities and internal audit work progress under IQAC. The IQAC coordinator enquired suggestion from IQAC member regarding the quality initiatives to be",
