    "section": "page 2",
    "text": "incorporated. Smt Deepa A K suggested the importance of peer reviewed publications as the part of accreditation process. Dr. Smitha P suggested the importance of curriculum gap analysis and systematic gap filling for the concerned courses . She also posted out the importance of Faculty development programs for faculty quality improvement. Mr. Rabeek suggested to strengthen the activities of other forum along with IEEE and IEDC. He also pointed out the importance of internships. Placement coordinator talked about present change in company offers, where job offers are only provided after few months internships. He also pointed out the importance of giving awareness of students regarding paid and un-paid internships. The placement coordinator also presented the details of technical and soft skill based training given to the students. Dr Madhusoodhanan Nair suggested the importance of industry exposure for students. Sri Hrishikesh , student representative pointed out the importance of creating incubation cell . He also suggested incubation cell should be created in such a way that it should be beneficial for all the branches in the institute. Finally, the meeting ended with the vote of thanks by CS department IQAC representative at 4 PM. Signature of Members present: 1.Dr .Smitha Dharan, Principal, CE Chengannur-IQAC Chair person 2. Mr. Bony Thomas, Scientist E, Electronics Regional Test Laboratory -Member Industry 3. Mr. Biju C Thomas, Chief consultant &Managing Director, Prime builders &Architects, Chengannur 4. Mrs. Deepa A K, Secretary, WIE Affinity Group IEEE Kerala Section. 5. Mr. Muhammed Rabeeh N, Co-Founder Electree Energy Solutions –Member Alumini 6. Dr. Laila D, HOD EC Department 7. Dr. Manju S Nair, HOD CS Department 8. Dr. Rajesh VG, HOD General Engineering 9. Dr. Raju M, Placement officer 10. Dr Madhusoodhanan Nair, HOD Applied science department 11. Mr. Vinod PR, Assistant Professor, Computer Engg ,PTA Secretary 12. Dr. DeepaJ, Professor, EC 