    "title": "Rules_For_Assigning_Student_Activity_Points.pdf",
    "section": "page 1",
    "text": "RULES FOR ASSIGNING ACTIVITY POINTS Encouraging the extra and co curricular activities of B.Tech & B.Arch students APJ ABDUL KALAM TECHNOLOGICAL UNIVERSITY KTU Academics",
    "metadata": {
