    "text": "Table of Contents 15. A SURVEY OF TECHNOLOGIES FOR ENHANCING ALUMNI-STUDENT- FACULTY NETWORKS Sreelekshmi A, Nijin K Varghese, Grace Mary K S, Vinod R, Dr Shani Raj ..............15 16. AUTO SPAXE : AN IOT BASED SMART PARKING APPLICATION Hilal Kalam A, Adwaith S Gopal, Gokul G Nair, Pranav PJ, Adarsh Ajay, Vishnu S kumar 16 17. MAYA : AN INTELLIGENT IMAGE CLASSIFICATION AND DISTRIBU- TION SYSTEM Nihal Muhammed Riyaz, Nived G, Shaniya N, Shabana Mol .............................. 17 18. AI-POWERED LEGAL ASSISTANCE - A REVIEW OF CHALLENGES, EXISTING SOLUTIONS, AND FUTURE DIRECTIONS Chaithanya Shaji, Ayisha Nahida Poovalappil, Gemima V.A, Mahira P ...................18 19. GPS BASED TRACKING SYSTEM FOR COLLEGE BUS Sharoon Rafeek, Asst.Prof Munthas TK, Muhammed Shuaib M, Sahal Shaz K, Salmanul Farizi NK ...................................................................................... 19 20. MULTI MODEL KIDNEY DISEASE PREDICTION SYSTEM Aysha Diya P A, Navya P, Ananda K, Aparna T S, Asst. Prof. Anupama K .............20 21. OPTICAL CHARACTER RECOGNITION OF MALAYALAM HANDWRIT- TEN TEXTS Adhwaith A M, Irin Jossy, Mahima Rachel Bijoy, Nikitha Liz Koshy, Sreelekshmi K R.....21 22. AI-DRIVEN PRECISION AGRICULTURE: CROP DETECTION, DISEASE PREDICTION, AND WEATHER FORECASTING WITH AGRIGUARD Ann Mathew, Navaneeth Rajesh, Neha Susan Aby, Pranoy Kurian Roy, Ms. Jeshmol PJ .. 22 23. AUTOMATIC LIVE ENGAGEMENT DETECTION OF STUDENTS DUR- ING ONLINE MEETING Aadhil Muhammed N, Adil Bin Anwar, Amith Kurian Joseph, Arun Kumar S, Swathi S .. 23 24. SPACECRAFT POSE ESTIMATOR Arjun R, Sreevenmathi D, Sabeena K, Surya S ........................................... 24 25. HOSPITALITY ANALYTICS USING POWER BI Arjun TP, Dr.Sabeena K .................................................................25 26. A REVIEW ON FOREST FIRE PREDICTION USING MACHINE LEARN- ING TECHNIQUES Anugrah R K, Geetha S ..................................................................26 27. PRESERVING THE