    "url": "https://ihrd.ac.in/images/stories/admin25/IHRDNRIP25.pdf",
    "title": "IHRDNRIP25.pdf",
    "section": "page 7",
    "text": "III. COURSE FEES HOME University IHRD The fee CfoOrL LNEGRI seats in B.Tech coursFeYsU GfoPr the academic year 2025-26 is Quota Quota ES DISCIPLI fixed by the Government/IHRD. No feeN E exemption or concession will be allowed to candidates seeking admission under NRI quota under any circumstances. 1. The Tuition Fee and Refundable Deposit prescribed for the NRI seats for 2025-2026 are as shown below. (These rates are applicable subject to any modifications ordered by the Government of Kerala /IHRD). Tuition Fee per year * fees may be varied subject to the approval of the Government 5",
