    "source": "pdf",
    "url": "https://ihrd.ac.in/images/stories/admin25/IHRDNRIP25.pdf",
    "title": "IHRDNRIP25.pdf",
    "section": "page 17",
    "text": "4. Last date for receipt of application, date of publication of rank list, admission schedule, date of closure of NRI admission etc. will be separately notified by the Director, IHRD through the official website of IHRD/colleges concerned. 5. All communication and notifications related to NRI admissions, including rank list, details of allotment, time schedule of admission etc. will be published only on the official websites of engineering colleges concerned/IHRD. No separate memo will be sent to the selected or University FYUGP waitlisted candidates. Failure to report for admission as per the announced DISCIPLI time schedule will lead to forfeit of the claNiEm for admission. 6. Any other matters not specifically covered in this prospectus will be decided based on the provisions for the same in the KEAM 2025 prospectus, by the Director, IHRD. 7. This prospectus is subject to modification based on decisions made by the IHRD authorities, the Government of Kerala, AICTE, and APJ Abdul Kalam Technological University (KTU), without prior intimation to the candidates. Section III(4) of this prospectus is subject to further decisions by the Admission Supervisory Committee (ASC) and Fee Regulatory Committee (FRC) for professional colleges of Kerala, if any. Place : Thiruvananthapuram DIRECTOR Date : 28.04.2025 15",
